sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Carousel Management Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant FS as Media Storage
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open carousel page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query slides ordered by position
    DB-->>LW: Slide list
    LW-->>UI: Render table and slide form

    User->>UI: Create/update slide
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Insert/update slide metadata and position
    LW->>FS: Store/replace slide image
    DB-->>LW: Persisted slide
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh list

    User->>UI: Move slide up/down
    UI->>LW: moveUp(id) / moveDown(id)
    LW->>DB: Swap positions with adjacent slide
    DB-->>LW: Updated ordering
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + re-render order

    User->>UI: Delete slide
    UI->>LW: deleteSlide(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete slide
    LW->>FS: Remove media
    DB-->>LW: Deleted
    LW-->>UI: Success toast
